  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<align=center><size=150%><b>HOW TO PLAY</b></size></align>\n\n<align=center><size=120%><b>CONTROLS</b></size></align>\n\u2022
    <b>Move:</b> Left/Right Arrow Keys\n\u2022 <b>Climb:</b> Up Arrow Key\n\u2022
    <b>Slide/Crouch:</b> Down Arrow Key\n\u2022 <b>Jump:</b> A\n\u2022 <b>Parkour:</b>
    S\n\u2022 <b>Trick:</b> D\n\u2022 <b>Trick:</b> Shift\n\n\u2022 <b>Restart Level:</b>
    R\n\n<align=center><size=120%><b>MECHANICS</b></size></align>\n\u2022 <b>Vault
    & Kong:</b> Hold S while moving toward an obstacle to automatically clear it.\n\u2022
    <b>Tricks:</b> Tap D right before hitting an obstacle to perform a Trick Vault.
    Tricks are slower and far more dangerous, but they are the absolute easiest way
    to build up your Flow Meter! Miss the timing, and you will wipe out. TIP: try
    pressing the trick input earlier than you'd think\n\u2022 <b>Springboard:</b>
    Jump <i>during</i> a vault (not a trick) to launch yourself up off the obstacle.\n\u2022
    <b>Wall Scramble:</b> Hold Forward + Up against a flat wall to run up it.\n\u2022
    <b>Ledge Grab:</b> Fall or scramble near a ledge to automatically hang.\n\n<align=center><size=120%><b>FLOW
    SYSTEM</b></size></align>\n\u2022 Keep moving fast and landing tricks to build
    your Flow Meter!\n\u2022 As your Flow Meter increases, your <b>base running speed
    and top speed</b> will get significantly faster.\n\u2022 <b>Flow Burst:</b> When
    you have enough meter, press Shift for an instant burst of max speed."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: e73a58f6e2794ae7b1b7e50b7fb811b0, type: 2}
